Hebrew-Romanized 
================

A module and helper script to convert romanized hebrew to actual hebrew text.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

   Tie::Hash::Default  (from this very repository)

